Jul 3rd, 2002 - wth 0.4.3
    new option to settime using the internal DCF77 receiver
    wind deviation data is now read (documentation leak), data decoding modified
    some minor bugs, code face lifting

Jan 7th, 2002 - wth 0.4.2 ready
    The newest version of wth supports xmlrpc for communication. 
    By this a full implmentation of the WS2000 weatherstation
    protocol using xml remote procedure calls (xmlrpc) has been added.


